                               other tuning
                  06.02.04 jp  CustNum for memo             
                  15.04.04/aam index CustName removed
                  20.03.06/aam use proper index for find etc.
                  18.04.06/aam use payments.p instead of nnlasu.p
                  16.06.06/aam ClaimState instead of ClaimQty
